webpackJsonp([0xc7bfda632b4c],{5307:function(e,t){e.exports={data:{post:{html:'<p><a href="http://andrea.editthispage.com/2001/07/30">Do not</a> trust a physicist with your hair dryer, or any other electrical appliances. Some things are best left to engineers.</p>\n<p>"Bildungsurlaub" is paid time off for continuing education. I asked my boss if I could have Bildungsurlaub to learn <a href="http://www.vim.org">vi</a>, but he turned me down.</p>\n<p>I\'ll bet the Mariners wish they could play the Twins every night.</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.fcstpauli.de">FC St. Pauli</a> opened their Bundesliga season with a 0-0 tie to Hertha BSC Berlin. They\'ll probably need 40 points to keep from being demoted, and with a budget of just DM 11 million, that\'s the best anyone can hope for. One down, 39 to go.</p>\n<p>Mama\'s out of town all week, so Christopher and I will be fending for ourselves until Friday evening.</p>',fields:{title:"Short Circuit",date:"31 Jul 2001",url:"https://papascott.de/2001-07-31-short-circuit/"}}},pathContext:{slug:"/2001-07-31-short-circuit/",prev:{fields:{title:"Mama State",date:"30 Jul 2001",slug:"/2001-07-30-mama-state/"}},next:{fields:{title:"Video Killed the Radio Star",date:"01 Aug 2001",slug:"/2001-08-01-video-killed-the-radio-star/"}}}}}});
